OL,3,CGerman football boss Julian Nagelsmann
OL,4,Cslams 'racist' survey
OL,6,FJulian Nagelsmann said he has been
OL,7,Fleft "shocked" by an "absolutely
OL,8,Fracist" survey asking if people would
OL,9,Fprefer more white players on his team.
OL,11,FReleased by German state broadcaster
OL,12,FARD, the survey of 1,304 randomly
OL,13,Fselected people found that 21% would
OL,14,Fprefer it if more players with white
OL,15,Fskin played for Germany.
