OL,3,CGerman football boss Julian Nagelsmann
OL,4,Cslams 'racist' survey
OL,6,FThe national team's coach agreed with
OL,7,Fcomments from midfielder Joshua
OL,8,FKimmich stating that the survey was
OL,9,F"racist" and that it was "madness for
OL,10,Fa public broadcaster to ask such a
OL,11,Fquestion."
OL,13,FSpeaking to reporters at the team's
OL,14,Ftraining camp for the , he said: "I
OL,15,Fthought about it briefly and I have
OL,16,Fthe feeling that we need to wake up a
OL,17,Fbit."
