OL,3,CGerman football boss Julian Nagelsmann
OL,4,Cslams 'racist' survey
OL,6,FHe added: "There are people in Europe
OL,7,Fwho've had to flee because of war,
OL,8,Feconomic factors, environmental
OL,9,Fdisasters, people who simply want to
OL,10,Fbe taken in.
OL,12,F"We have to ask what are we doing at
OL,13,Fthe moment? We in Germany are doing
OL,14,Fvery, very well, and when we say
OL,15,Fsomething like that, I think it's
OL,16,Fcrazy how we turn a blind eye and
OL,17,Fsimply block out such things."
