OL,3,CGerman football boss Julian Nagelsmann
OL,4,Cslams 'racist' survey
OL,6,FNagelsmann said Kimmich was correct
OL,7,Fwhen he said a football team can be a
OL,8,Frole model for how different cultures,
OL,9,Freligious backgrounds and skin colors
OL,10,Fcan join in a group to work together
OL,11,Ffor major goals.
OL,13,F"I always find it bizarre that we all
OL,14,Fgo on vacation to get to know other
OL,15,Fcultures and then other cultures come
OL,16,Fhere and we complain about it. It's
OL,17,Fbizarre," Nagelsmann said. "So, I
OL,18,Fcan't go on vacation then, I always
OL,19,Fhave to stay where I am."
