OL,3,CGerman football boss Julian Nagelsmann
OL,4,Cslams 'racist' survey
OL,6,FNagelsmann also agreed with Kimmich
OL,7,Fthat he does not want to do without
OL,8,Fany of the players he nominated in his
OL,9,Fsquad, which includes black players.
OL,11,F"It's good as it is," Nagelsmann said.
OL,12,F"We're playing a European Championship
OL,13,Ffor everyone in the country. And
OL,14,Fanyone who can play top football is
OL,15,Finvited to be a national player and
OL,16,Fgive their all for their country. And
OL,17,Fthat's what we're doing. And I hope I
OL,18,Fnever have to read about such a
OL,19,F(expletive) survey again."
